github.repositories().orderBy("stars")
---
GET https://api.github.com/search/repositories?sort=stars&order=asc


github.repositories().orderBy("stars", "desc")
---
GET https://api.github.com/search/repositories?sort=stars&order=desc


github.repositories().orderBy("updated")
---
GET https://api.github.com/search/repositories?sort=updated&order=asc


github.repositories(.language == "python").orderBy("forks", "desc")
---
GET https://api.github.com/search/repositories?q=language%3Apython&sort=forks&order=desc


github.users().orderBy("followers", "desc")
---
GET https://api.github.com/search/users?sort=followers&order=desc
